# VOXEL DOMINION does not require any frontend secrets.
# The Intelligent Contract is the backend; the static frontend reads and writes
# the live contract through genlayer-js. Wallet signing happens in the browser.
#
# Deploying your own instance only needs a funded GenLayer account in the CLI:
#   genlayer account import --name voxel-dominion --private-key 0x...
#   genlayer deploy --contract contracts/contract.py
# Then put the deployed address and tx hash in frontend/src/lib/contract.ts.
